Name: Monkey GO Happy
About the game: Over 75 stages of puzzling fun to complete! Monkey GO Happy from Pencilkids is an internet sensation that has reached millions of players online. Now the original 5 Monkey GO Happy games have been compiled into one great app. Features: - over 75 beautifully designed stages - 30 Hats to dress up your monkey - 7 different monkeys to choose from - Ad FREE - NO In-app purchases - Automatic save progress Instructions: Tap on objects and locations on the screen. Drag items to specific spots to solve puzzles and more!
